    <h1 class="page-title">Shayantha <em>Das</em></h1>
    <p>I'm a Data Analyst and Digital Marketer based in Chattogram, Bangladesh. With 3+ years of hands-on experience, I help organizations and startups unlock the stories hidden in their data — and then use those insights to build marketing strategies that drive real, measurable growth.</p>
    <p>My background sits at the intersection of two disciplines most people keep separate: the precision of data science and the creativity of marketing. I believe the most powerful business decisions come when both are working together.</p>
    <p>Outside of work, I write about data and marketing on this blog, mentor aspiring analysts, and drink an unreasonable amount of tea while exploring new datasets.</p>
